# VideoTube - Backend

REST API for VideoTube platform built with Node.js and Express.

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- JWT Authentication
- Cloudinary (video/image storage)

## Features
- User registration, login, JWT auth
- Video upload, update, delete
- Comments and likes system
- Channel and subscription management

## Setup
npm install
npm run dev
